Description
-----------

Software rendered [antialiasing](Antialiasing "Antialiasing") for use when using the [aviDemo](AviDemo_%28console_command%29 "AviDemo (console command)") command.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    com_aviDemoSamples [int]

Parameters
----------

-   [int] - A positive value for the amount shots to blend into a single frame.

